default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe “next steps” consultation document indicates that some modifications will be made to the April
default 2013 proposals. However, regarding
default the three issues 
defaultabove 
defaultour view is that our concerns largely still remain
default as they were.
default   
defaultThe residence test default8.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe “next s
defaultteps” document 
defaultat 2.11 – 2.17 
defaultindicates residence test modifications.  While we welcome these changes, they do not adequately address the substance and scope of the matters we raised in our response on this issue.
default 
default 
defaultLegal aid for prisonersdefault9.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
